title: International New York Times Nov 20
description: The International New York Times is an English language international newspaper. It combines the resources of its own correspondents with those of The New York Times and is printed at 38 sites throughout the world, for sale in more than 160 countries and territories. Based in Paris since 1887,[2] the newspaper is part of The New York Times Company. From 1967 it was published as the International Herald Tribune, but was renamed on October 15, 2013
